en dÄ±ÅŸÄ±nda herhangi bir ama&ccedil;la kullanÄ±lamaz. </span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#002060;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;\">Kiralananda, kiracÄ±, eÅŸi ve &ccedil;ocuklarÄ±nÄ±n dÄ±ÅŸÄ±nda kimse kalamaz. </span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#002060;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;\">Kira bedelleri,&nbsp; her ayÄ±n beÅŸinci g&uuml;n&uuml; akÅŸamÄ±na kadar, kiralayanÄ±n &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip; bankasÄ±, &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip; Åžubesindeki &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip; numaralÄ± hesabÄ±na yatÄ±rÄ±lacaktÄ±r.&nbsp; Kira parasÄ±nÄ±n baÅŸka bir ÅŸubeden havale edilmesi halinde, aynÄ± s&uuml;re i&ccedil;inde hesapta olacak ÅŸekilde iÅŸlem yaptÄ±rÄ±lacak olup, aksi durumda temerr&uuml;t h&uuml;k&uuml;mleri uygulanacaktÄ±r. Bir ayÄ±n kira parasÄ±nÄ±n &ouml;denmemesi halinde d&ouml;nem sonuna kadar iÅŸleyecek kira paralarÄ±nÄ±n t&uuml;m&uuml; muacceliyet kazanacaktÄ±r. </span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#002060;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;\">KiralananÄ±n kapÄ±cÄ±/kaloriferci, yakÄ±t ve genel giderleri kiracÄ± tarafÄ±ndan &ouml;denecektir. </span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#002060;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;\">KapÄ±lar, pencereler, sÄ±hh&icirc; tesisat ara&ccedil;larÄ± saÄŸlam, tam ve kullanÄ±lmaya elveriÅŸli olarak teslim edilmiÅŸtir. </span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#002060;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;\">KiracÄ±, kiralananÄ± &ouml;zenle kullanacak; kiralayan da gerekli onarÄ±mlarÄ±, kiracÄ±nÄ±n uyarÄ±sÄ±ndan itibaren on g&uuml;n i&ccedil;inde -teknik olanaksÄ±zlar hari&ccedil;-&nbsp; yaptÄ±racaktÄ±r.</span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#002060;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;\">KiracÄ±, elektrik aboneliÄŸini kendi adÄ±na yaptÄ±racak, s&ouml;zleÅŸme sonunda hesabÄ± kestirerek, buna iliÅŸkin makbuz fotokopisini kiralayana verecektir. </span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#002060;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;\">KiracÄ±, &uuml;&ccedil; g&uuml;n i&ccedil;inde, aile beyannamesini mahalle muhtarlÄ±ÄŸÄ±na verecektir. </span></li>\r\n				<li style=\"color:#002060;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;\">S&ouml;zleÅŸmeden doÄŸacak uyuÅŸmazlÄ±klardan dolayÄ±, EskiÅŸehir &nbsp;Mahkemeleri ve icra m&uuml;d&uuml;rl&uuml;kleri yetkili olacaktÄ±r. </span></li>\r\n			</ol>\r\n\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"color:#002060;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;\">Ä°ÅŸbu, on sekiz genel ve on &ouml;zel koÅŸuldan oluÅŸan s&ouml;zleÅŸmeyi, h&uuml;r iradelerimizle iki n&uuml;sha olarak imzaladÄ±k. &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;..Tarih.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"color:#002060;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;\">KiracÄ±:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Kiralayan:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"color:#002060;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;\">(imza)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nb